# Project context

Gatsby documentation site for the **advanced-logger** npm package (not the library source).

- Content: `src/pages/*.md` with frontmatter `template: <name>` → `src/templates/<name>.tsx`
- Nav order: `src/settings/nav-menu.md` (`ordering` must match page `title` values)
- Run locally: `npm run develop`; verify: `npm run build`
- Full architecture and pitfalls: see root `AGENTS.md`

Keep changes scoped: doc text in markdown, layout in templates/components, routing in `gatsby-node.ts`.
